        "TileImage": "$($repository 360edd56-1b2a-4624-9b6c-2d866a7c7cc0).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. Your targets today are social media influencer Jacqueline Wealthy and two members of her entourage, Loretta Thompson and Ashley Montague. The three are no strangers to controversy, and are currently laying low after the suspicious death of one of their collaborators during a trip to Spain.\r\rJacqueline has been spotted around the island with her manager, while her two friends are enjoying the beach. The client would like their little vacation extended permanently. Happy hunting.",
